name: Hannah Fry - Textual Inversion
description:
This ti was requested by @beninar101

Hannah Fry is a British mathematician, author, and television presenter. She is known for her work in the field of applied mathematics and has a passion for communicating complex mathematical concepts to a wider audience. Fry has made numerous appearances on television and radio, where she explains mathematical principles and their applications in everyday life. She has presented several documentaries, including "City in the Sky" and "Magic Numbers: Hannah Fry's Mysterious World of Maths," which aired on the BBC.
